theorem P3_union {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X}
    (hA : Topology.P3 A) (hB : Topology.P3 B) :
    Topology.P3 (A ∪ B) := by
  dsimp [Topology.P3] at hA hB ⊢
  intro x hx
  rcases hx with hAx | hBx
  · have hxA : x ∈ interior (closure A) := hA hAx
    have hsubset : interior (closure A) ⊆ interior (closure (A ∪ B)) := by
      have hcl : closure A ⊆ closure (A ∪ B) := by
        have : A ⊆ A ∪ B := Set.subset_union_left _ _
        exact closure_mono this
      exact interior_mono hcl
    exact hsubset hxA
  · have hxB : x ∈ interior (closure B) := hB hBx
    have hsubset : interior (closure B) ⊆ interior (closure (A ∪ B)) := by
      have hcl : closure B ⊆ closure (A ∪ B) := by
        have : B ⊆ A ∪ B := Set.subset_union_right _ _
        exact closure_mono this
      exact interior_mono hcl
    exact hsubset hxB

theorem interior_closure_P2 {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    Topology.P2 (interior (closure A)) := by
  have h_open : IsOpen (interior (closure A)) := isOpen_interior
  simpa using
    Topology.isOpen_imp_P2 (X := X) (A := interior (closure A)) h_open
